item.title: You Won't Believe How Easy It Is To Check If You've Won Roll Up The Rim To Win!
item.description: You Won’t Believe How Easy It Is To Check If You’ve Won Roll Up The Rim To Win! Roll Up The Rim To Win is a fun and exciting way to win amazing prizes from your favorite coffee shop, Tim Hortons. Every year, millions of Canadians take part in this contest and try their luck at winning one of the many prizes offered. But how do you know if you’ve won?
